Silent Features.
1.Implemented completely in MVC Structure.
2.Used Jquery ajax for form submissions in the application
3.Database structure is included as image (database-model.png). open it to see the complete database structure.
4.Used Pagination
5.Implemented APC cache for getting and storing images from the flickr
6.Documentation
7.Coding standards which I followed
8.Finally and important one "Architecture Design"

Hope you will Enjoy the architecture.







